sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant D as Dashboard
    participant A as FastAPI /demo/inject-spike
    participant S as spike_injector
    participant P as preprocessor
    participant M as IF + LSTM
    participant DB as SQLite

    User->>D: Choose mode, magnitude, duration
    D->>A: POST /demo/inject-spike {series_key, mode, ...}
    A->>S: make_clean_copy(series)
    A->>S: inject_spike(mid-series, mode)
    S-->>A: modified series + ground-truth labels
    A->>P: scale + create_windows + features
    P-->>A: windows, features, window_3d
    A->>M: score full series (batch)
    M-->>A: per-window scores + flags
    A->>DB: log_prediction + log_alert (first detection)
    A-->>D: SpikeInjectionResponse {predictions, n_anomalous}
    D-->>User: Show injected anomaly detected on chart
